These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-1::.
2 different games are played: monopoly, bridge
1. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |
| Game   | monopoly | bridge |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, iced-tea
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |
| Beverage   | lemonade | iced-tea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, chinese
1. the dutch is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |   2   |
| Nationality   | chinese | dutch |

 #################################

 
